        <updateDate>2015-04-30T21:20:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill amends the Fair Labor Standards Act of 1938 to redefine &quot;oppressive child labor,&quot; for purposes of child labor prohibitions, to include the employment of any employee under age 18 who has direct contact with tobacco plants or dried tobacco leaves.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
